Category:Unidentified Jedi of the New Jedi Order

nodes.text: This male Rodian was trained as a Jedi in the New Jedi Order. During the Swarm War this individual was training to become a Jedi at the Ossus Academy. When Chiss Aristocra Chaf'orm'bintrano visited the academy, the apprentice was partaking in a game of Skorch. He may also have been the Rodian seen at the Conclave on Zonama Sekot.
